929
01:32:34,805 --> 01:32:36,348
¿Herr Lieberman?

930
01:32:42,604 --> 01:32:44,148
Herr Lieberman...

931
01:32:46,942 --> 01:32:48,485
No es Mozart, doctor.

932
01:32:51,238 --> 01:32:52,781
No es Picasso.

933
01:32:53,907 --> 01:32:56,618
No es un genio que
enriquecería al mundo...

934
01:32:59,079 --> 01:33:03,375
...sino un niñito solitario,
con un padre autoritario,

935
01:33:04,668 --> 01:33:06,211
...un oficial de aduanas

936
01:33:06,503 --> 01:33:09,465
...que tuviera 52
